data.description: Welcome to Sunway Knolls!  Close to Shaw AFB and town, this 1905 sq ft 3 bedroom 2 bath home has plenty of space for your family.  Eat-in kitchen as well as a formal ding area.  Fireplace in the family room. Huge back yard for the kids to play and fully fenced in if you have pets.  Seller is offering a $5000 allowance to buy down buyers rate, use for closing cost or floor allowance.
